784
01:03:25,084 --> 01:03:27,681
让我尽量谈到最好的条件?
to make the best terms that I can huh?

785
01:03:27,763 --> 01:03:29,601
我积蓄有限 福尔摩斯先生
I have limited resources Mr. Holmes.

786
