791
01:03:41,783 --> 01:03:44,555
为我向您的教母问好
My best wishes to your Godmother.

792
01:03:49,680 --> 01:03:51,305
Eva小姐
Lady Eva?

793
01:03:53,576 --> 01:03:56,042
你必须相信福尔摩斯先生
You must trust Mr. Holmes

794
01:03:56,116 --> 01:03:57,360
和他的方法
and his methods.

795
01:03:57,438 --> 01:03:58,790
完全地信任
Absolutely.

796
01:03:58,865 --> 01:04:01,153
Hudson太太会送你出门
Mrs. Hudson will see you out.

797
01:04:11,736 --> 01:04:13,395
那位年轻女士 福尔摩斯
That young lady, Holmes,

798
01:04:13,476 --> 01:04:15,942
显然得到了极大的关照
must be treated with infinite care

799
01:04:16,015 --> 01:04:18,303
一点都不像你最近其它的恶作剧
unlike your other recent escapade.

800
01:04:18,381 --> 01:04:20,077
华生
Oh Watson,

801
01:04:20,156 --> 01:04:23,422
她能独自前来已经是鼓足了勇气
it took some nerve for her to come here alone.

802
01:04:27,844 --> 01:04:29,753
我相信Eva小姐
It is my belief that Lady Eva

803
01:04:29,827 --> 01:04:31,214
和Milverton的侍女
and the Milverton housemaid

804
01:04:31,288 --> 01:04:32,640
有某个共同点
have something in common.

805
01:04:32,714 --> 01:04:33,958
是什么呢?
And what is that?

806
01:04:34,037 --> 01:04:35,839
活力
Juice.

807
01:04:35,915 --> 01:04:38,488
华生 活力
Watson juice

808
01:04:38,560 --> 01:04:41,549
在面对逆境的时候
in the face of adversity.

809
01:04:41,621 --> 01:04:46,139
现在 Milverton先生
Now Mr. Milverton.

810
01:05:01,869 --> 01:05:04,406
唉呦 唉呦 唉呦
Well, well, well.

811
01:05:09,348 --> 01:05:10,936
Eva?
Eva?

812
01:05:13,314 --> 01:05:14,843
Eva?
Eva?

813
01:05:24,412 --> 01:05:26,000
Eva?
Eva?

814
01:05:30,153 --> 01:05:31,991
Eva?
Eva?

815
01:05:47,965 --> 01:05:49,874
Lottie
Lottie.

816
01:05:58,820 --> 01:06:01,809
真高兴见到你
I am so glad to see you.

817
01:06:01,881 --> 01:06:04,941
巴黎不是答案
Paris wasn't the answer.

818
01:06:05,012 --> 01:06:07,478
找到你真不容易
You've been hard to find.

819
01:06:09,117 --> 01:06:10,575
你在干什么?
What were you doing?

820
01:06:10,649 --> 01:06:12,593
我睡着了
I fell asleep.

821
01:06:12,666 --> 01:06:15,406
Johnson告诉了我你叔叔Charles的事
Johnson told me about your Uncle Charles.

822
01:06:15,483 --> 01:06:16,763
我很遗憾
I'm so sorry.

823
01:06:16,841 --> 01:06:20,351
我留在这里是为了安慰Diana 但是...
I stayed here to comfort Diana but

824
01:06:20,424 --> 01:06:23,093
这房子太悲伤了
this house is so sad.

825
01:06:45,856 --> 01:06:48,358
我们6点半再登门
We'll call again at 6:30.

826
01:06:48,430 --> 01:06:50,268
C.A.M
C-A-M.

827
01:07:27,638 --> 01:07:28,432
你准备好了吗?
You ready?

828
01:07:28,507 --> 01:07:29,506
是的
Yes.

829
01:07:39,849 --> 01:07:44,012
夏洛克 福尔摩斯先生
Mr. Sherlock Holmes.

830
01:07:50,565 --> 01:07:53,684
这位先生...这样谨慎吗?
This gentlemen is it discreet?

831
01:07:53,765 --> 01:07:59,328
华生是我的朋友和搭档
Dr. Watson is my friend and partner.

832
01:07:59,401 --> 01:08:02,947
纯粹出于对你委托人利益的考虑
It is purely in the interest of your client

833
01:08:03,019 --> 01:08:05,130
我表示反对
that I protest it.

834
01:08:05,211 --> 01:08:08,366
这件事很棘手
The matter is so very delicate.

835
01:08:08,446 --> 01:08:11,885
华生医生已经想到这点了
Dr. Watson has already thought of that.

836
01:08:14,117 --> 01:08:15,741
请允许我?
May I?

837
01:08:15,822 --> 01:08:18,419
谢谢
Oh thank you.

838
01:08:29,598 --> 01:08:32,302
那我们就来谈买卖吧
Then we may proceed to business.

839
01:08:32,381 --> 01:08:33,804
你在你的留言里说
You said in your note

840
01:08:33,877 --> 01:08:37,423
你是Eva女士的全权代表
that you are acting for the Lady Eva,

841
01:08:37,495 --> 01:08:42,325
那你有权接受我的条件吗?
are you empowered to accept my terms?

842
01:08:46,784 --> 01:08:48,835
你的条件是什么?
What are your terms?

843
01:08:58,335 --> 01:09:01,430
7000磅?
Seven thousand pounds?

844
01:09:01,500 --> 01:09:04,381
另一种选择呢?
And the alternative?

845
01:09:04,457 --> 01:09:05,435
亲爱的先生
My dear sir,

846
01:09:05,472 --> 01:09:08,205
讨论这个我很不好受
it is painful for me to discuss it

847
01:09:08,285 --> 01:09:11,962
但是我可以说
but I can say

848
01:09:12,042 --> 01:09:16,729
这是出于极为慎重的考量
that all of this is done with most careful consideration

849
01:09:16,809 --> 01:09:20,972
如果在14日那天没有付钱
and if the money is not paid on the 14th then there certainly

850
01:09:21,052 --> 01:09:23,198
那么18日那天也不会有什么婚礼
will be no marriage on the 1 8th.

851
01:09:26,166 --> 01:09:30,086
我们当然熟悉那些信的内容
We are, of course, familiar with the contents of these letters.

852
01:09:30,167 --> 01:09:32,455
我们会建议我们的委托人
We shall advise our client

853
01:09:32,533 --> 01:09:35,830
把整个故事告诉她未来的丈夫
to tell her future husband the whole story

854
01:09:35,908 --> 01:09:38,505
相信他的宽宏大量
and trust to his generosity.

855
01:09:38,586 --> 01:09:42,713
那你显然是不了解伯爵的为人
Well then you evidently do not know the Earl.

856
01:09:42,796 --> 01:09:45,820
那些信里到底有什么能伤人的地方
What harm is there in these letters?

857
01:09:45,892 --> 01:09:48,489
遣词很活泼
They are sprightly

858
01:09:48,571 --> 01:09:50,444
非常活泼
very sprightly.

859
01:09:50,520 --> 01:09:52,880
女士是位有文笔的写信人
The lady was a charming correspondent.

860
01:09:52,955 --> 01:09:55,101
但是我向你保证Dovercourt伯爵
But I assure you the Earl of Dovercourt

861
01:09:55,181 --> 01:09:58,276
不会欣赏它们
will fail to appreciate them.

862
01:09:58,347 --> 01:09:59,935
不过 如果你不这么想
However, if you think otherwise,

863
01:10:00,017 --> 01:10:01,440
这不过是桩生意
it's purely a matter of business.

864
01:10:01,513 --> 01:10:04,708
如果你认为这对你的委托人是最好的
If you think it in the best interests of your client

865
01:10:04,783 --> 01:10:08,292
那掏出那么一大笔钱的确太蠢了
then it would indeed be foolish to pay so large a sum of money.

866
01:10:08,367 --> 01:10:10,798
你说得太快了
You go too fast.

867
01:10:10,871 --> 01:10:15,807
在这么一件棘手的事上 我们当然是要尽力避免丑闻
We would certainly make every effort to avoid scandal in so delicate a matter.

868
01:10:15,881 --> 01:10:20,079
我肯定你也是这么想的
I felt sure that you see it in that light.

869
01:10:31,154 --> 01:10:32,850
你这该死的
Damn you.

870
01:10:34,181 --> 01:10:37,205
Eva小姐不是个富有的人
Lady Eva is not a wealthy woman.

871
01:10:37,277 --> 01:10:38,521
2000英镑
Two thousand pounds

872
01:10:38,599 --> 01:10:41,694
是她所有的积蓄
would be total drain on her resources.

873
01:10:41,765 --> 01:10:45,345
你说的那个数字她完全负担不起
The sum you named utterly beyond her power.

874
01:10:46,775 --> 01:10:48,921
让我们以这个价钱赎回信吧
Return the letters at the price we indicate,

875
01:10:49,001 --> 01:10:50,459
我向你保证
I assure you,

876
01:10:50,531 --> 01:10:53,626
这是你能拿到的最高价
it is the highest you can get.

877
01:10:53,698 --> 01:10:56,687
你说那是小姐的所有积蓄也许是真的
What you say maybe true of the lady's resources

878
01:10:56,759 --> 01:10:59,391
但是一旦结婚
but the surely the occasion of her marriage

879
01:10:59,473 --> 01:11:02,094
不正是她的朋友和亲人
is it not a proper time for her friends and relations

880
01:11:02,131 --> 01:11:04,968
助她一臂之力的时候吗?
to make some little effort on her behalf?

881
01:11:08,657 --> 01:11:13,307
他们可能正犹豫送什么结婚礼物
They may hesitate as to an acceptable wedding present

882
01:11:13,388 --> 01:11:16,483
但是这一扎信
but this little bundle of letters

883
01:11:16,555 --> 01:11:18,049
带了的余兴
would bring more joy

884
01:11:18,120 --> 01:11:21,073
将远多于伦敦所有的宴会
than all the candelabras and butter dishes in London

885
01:11:21,147 --> 01:11:22,806
不是吗?
wouldn't it?

886
01:11:24,486 --> 01:11:26,668
这不可能
It is not possible.

887
01:11:26,748 --> 01:11:28,135
啊 天哪
Oh dear me then.

888
01:11:28,209 --> 01:11:29,833
真是不幸啊
How very unfortunate.

889
01:11:29,913 --> 01:11:36,616
我觉得小姐们都被糟糕地建议 不要去做什么尝试
I cannot help feeling that ladies are ill advised in not making an effort.

890
01:11:40,907 --> 01:11:42,455
看看这个
Look at this.

891
01:11:43,691 --> 01:11:45,979
这个属于...
This belongs to,

892
01:11:49,361 --> 01:11:54,222
也许不该告诉你们这是属于谁的
well perhaps it's hardly fair to tell you to whom it belongs

893
01:11:54,301 --> 01:11:57,594
直到明天早上它们到女士的丈夫手中
until tomorrow morning when it will be in the hands of the lady's husband.

894
01:11:57,676 --> 01:12:01,431
只是因为她筹不到这么一点小钱
And all because she will not find a beggarly sum

895
01:12:01,503 --> 01:12:03,554
原本是很容易办到的事
which she could easily do

896
01:12:03,625 --> 01:12:06,997
只要把她的一些钻石换成人工珠宝的就行
simply by turning some of her diamonds into paste.

897
01:12:07,069 --> 01:12:08,978
多么可惜啊!
It is such a pity!

898
01:12:09,052 --> 01:12:11,103
你或许在最近的晨报上
You may have noticed a small paragraph

899
01:12:11,174 --> 01:12:14,091
注意到一篇短讯
recently in the Morning Post.

900
01:12:14,167 --> 01:12:15,661
尊贵的Miles小姐和Dorking上校
The sudden end of the engagement

901
01:12:15,732 --> 01:12:19,132
突然终止了彼此的婚约
between the Honorable Miss Miles and Colonel Dorking?

902
01:12:19,211 --> 01:12:22,472
是啊 真是个不幸的结局
Yes and it's tragic consequences.

903
01:12:22,550 --> 01:12:24,423
你也可以把它称为谋杀
You can almost call it murder.

904
01:12:24,499 --> 01:12:28,389
你怎么回应此事呢 Milverton先生?
How do you answer for that Mr. Milverton?

905
01:12:28,465 --> 01:12:30,267
在那种情形下
How a man conducts himself

906
01:12:30,343 --> 01:12:32,110
一个人做出怎样的行为
under such circumstances

907
01:12:32,188 --> 01:12:35,283
都是他自己的决定
is a matter for himself alone.

908
01:12:35,353 --> 01:12:37,297
那是不义之财!
That is a monstrous accession.

909
01:12:37,371 --> 01:12:38,686
是你
It was you

910
01:12:38,763 --> 01:12:41,229
你一个人害死了他
and you alone who caused his death.

911
01:12:41,303 --> 01:12:44,813
就为了那点钱
And the sum involved niggardly.

912
01:12:44,886 --> 01:12:47,590
确实才1200磅
Indeed a mere twelve hundred pounds

913
01:12:47,669 --> 01:12:49,328
就可以解决所有的问题
would have settled the whole questions.

914
01:12:49,408 --> 01:12:52,218
很可惜 不是吗?
Pitiful isn't it?

915
01:12:52,296 --> 01:12:54,347
但是我发现福尔摩斯先生
And yet I find you Mr. Holmes,

916
01:12:54,418 --> 01:12:55,556
作为一个明白人
a man of sense,

917
01:12:55,636 --> 01:13:00,760
居然拿你们委托人全部未来和荣耀 和我谈条件
boggling over terms when the whole future and honor of your client is at stake.

918
01:13:00,797 --> 01:13:02,984
你让我很吃惊 真的很吃惊
You surprise me. You do really.

919
01:13:05,864 --> 01:13:08,853
找不到那么多钱
The money cannot be found.

920
01:13:08,926 --> 01:13:13,881
最好你接受我们提出的价钱
Surely it would be better for you to take the substantial sum we offer

921
01:13:13,956 --> 01:13:16,080
而不是毁了她的前程
than to ruin this young woman's career,

922
01:13:16,162 --> 01:13:18,106
不然什么也得不到
which can profit you in no way.

923
01:13:18,179 --> 01:13:20,848
那你就错了
But you're mistaken.

924
01:13:20,927 --> 01:13:24,604
曝光此事会间接使我
An exposure would profit me indirectly

925
01:13:24,685 --> 01:13:26,796
受到很大的益处
to a considerable degree.

926
01:13:26,877 --> 01:13:28,821
我还有八件 十件
I have eight or ten

927
01:13:28,894 --> 01:13:31,954
类似的事情要去谈
similar cases materializing.

928
01:13:32,025 --> 01:13:37,545
要是Eva小姐的不幸能成为事例流传开
If it is circulated that I have made a severe example of Lady Eva.

929
01:13:37,627 --> 01:13:39,429
会使其余的人
I'll shall find the rest

930
01:13:39,505 --> 01:13:41,486
更理智一些
much more open to reason.

931
01:13:41,558 --> 01:13:43,396
你们明白我的意思了?
Do you see my point?

932
01:13:53,282 --> 01:13:55,986
我们来看看这些信的内容
Let us see the contents of those letters.

933
01:14:05,285 --> 01:14:06,649
福尔摩斯先生
Mr. Holmes.

934
01:14:06,686 --> 01:14:10,681
福尔摩斯 我以为你会做些有创意的事情
Mr. Holmes I've been expecting you to do something original.

935
01:14:10,718 --> 01:14:13,242
这早就司空见惯了
This has been tried so often before.

936
01:14:13,279 --> 01:14:15,669
小Edward Kroft就是其中一个
Young Edward Kroft for one.

937
01:14:16,174 --> 01:14:17,348
Kroft?
Kroft?

938
