那个男仆Veitch
The footman Veitch

939
01:14:19,653 --> 01:14:22,155
替你挡下了本该射向你的子弹
who took the bullet that was rightfully yours.

940
01:14:22,228 --> 01:14:24,279
你调查过我
You've done some work on me.

941
01:14:24,350 --> 01:14:25,583
那你一定知道
So you must know

942
01:14:25,620 --> 01:14:28,656
没有什么能靠近伤害我
that nothing ever came of an attack on my person.

943
01:14:28,733 --> 01:14:30,429
我武装到了牙齿
I'm armed to the teeth

944
01:14:30,508 --> 01:14:33,045
一直是这样
at all times

945
01:14:33,116 --> 01:14:35,512
无时无刻不准备着使用武器
and I'm perfectly prepared to use my weapons

946
01:14:35,586 --> 01:14:38,919
我知道法律会保护我
and knowing that the law will support me.

947
01:14:40,945 --> 01:14:43,550
你或许有机会来检验一下这套理论
You may well have your chance to test your assumption.

948
01:14:50,721 --> 01:14:53,294
Hudson太太 别让人来打扰我
Mrs. Hudson I am not to be disturbed.

949
01:14:53,365 --> 01:14:54,265
走吧
Go.

950
01:14:58,652 --> 01:15:00,629
福尔摩斯 你不会真认为
Mr. Holmes surely you don't believe

951
01:15:00,666 --> 01:15:04,323
我会傻到把谋生的东西随身携带吧?
I'd be so foolish to carry my livelihood here in my pocket?

952
01:15:04,360 --> 01:15:07,091
只是为了确认一下 Milverton先生
Just making sure Mr. Milverton.

953
01:15:09,960 --> 01:15:12,391
那么 现在 先生们
Well now gentlemen,

954
01:15:12,464 --> 01:15:17,019
我今晚还有一两个小约会
I have one or two little interviews this evening

955
01:15:17,091 --> 01:15:20,044
从这到Hampstead还很远
and it's a long drive to Hampstead.

956
01:15:46,419 --> 01:15:52,219
有人给了Milverton一点教训
Now someone has dealt Milverton a blow.

957
01:15:56,125 --> 01:15:59,006
一个愤怒的丈夫
An outraged husband

958
01:15:59,082 --> 01:16:02,555
和其余在这个灰暗的城市里数以千计人一样
just as there are thousands in this grey city

959
01:16:02,631 --> 01:16:06,177
盼着Milverton去死
who crave Milverton's destruction

960
01:16:06,249 --> 01:16:08,574
或许会先我们一步
and may yet beat us to it.

961
01:16:13,415 --> 01:16:15,324
福尔摩斯?
Holmes?

962
01:16:15,398 --> 01:16:18,244
我和任何人一样爱好艺术
I'm as fond of art as any man

963
01:16:18,321 --> 01:16:20,918
但是你不认为在昨天的谈话之后...
but don't you think after yesterday's encounter...

964
01:16:20,999 --> 01:16:24,604
艺术离不开头脑
Art is bond to the brain

965
01:16:24,687 --> 01:16:28,269
特别是在做决定的时候
especially in moments of decision.

966
01:16:28,341 --> 01:16:30,938
我们了解了一些Milverton的情况
So we've learned something about Milverton.

967
01:16:31,019 --> 01:16:34,139
他的残忍无情很难被曝光
That he's ruthless is hardly a revelation.

968
01:16:34,220 --> 01:16:35,535
他的虚荣
And that of his vanity

969
01:16:35,611 --> 01:16:39,624
就是他的弱点
and to a certain his vulnerability.

970
01:16:39,661 --> 01:16:42,253
被砍坏的马车
I can see that the damage to his carriage

971
01:16:42,326 --> 01:16:43,950
也许让他有些不安
might have unsettled him.

972
01:16:44,031 --> 01:16:46,427
我们一定要利用这些事
We must exploit such things.

973
01:16:46,501 --> 01:16:47,878
肆无忌惮的蓄意破坏
Wanton vandalism.

974
01:16:47,914 --> 01:16:49,786
"盔甲上出现了裂缝" (他的防备有了漏洞)
Any chink in the armor.

975
01:16:52,067 --> 01:16:53,834
福尔摩斯先生
Mr. Holmes

976
01:16:53,911 --> 01:16:55,440
这是我的朋友
this is my friend

977
01:16:55,511 --> 01:16:57,349
尊敬的Charlotte Miles
the Honorable Charlotte Miles.

978
01:16:57,424 --> 01:16:58,633
这为是夏洛克福尔摩斯先生
Mr. Sherlock Holmes

979
01:16:58,712 --> 01:17:00,787
和他的搭档华生先生
and his partner Mr. Watson.

980
01:17:00,869 --> 01:17:04,024
Eva小姐能和您单独谈谈吗?
Lady Eva may speak privately to you?

981
01:17:12,767 --> 01:17:14,640
Miles太太
Mrs. Miles

982
01:17:14,715 --> 01:17:17,312
请接受我们的慰问
please accept our sympathy.

983
01:17:17,394 --> 01:17:18,923
福尔摩斯先生和我
Mr. Holmes and I

984
01:17:18,995 --> 01:17:20,904
都知道您的情况
are fully aware of your situation.

985
01:17:20,977 --> 01:17:22,744
很感谢你 华生医生
That is most kind of you Doctor Watson

986
01:17:22,821 --> 01:17:26,331
但人要带着自己的错误活下去
but one has to live with one's mistakes.

987
01:17:28,527 --> 01:17:30,780
他不肯让步
He was unyielding.

988
01:17:36,145 --> 01:17:38,256
现在 下一步
Now the next move

989
01:17:38,337 --> 01:17:41,527
需要你完全的配合
requires your delicate cooperation.

990
01:17:41,608 --> 01:17:43,031
我会按你说的做
I'll do anything you say Mr. Holmes.

991
01:17:43,104 --> 01:17:45,215
舞会在哪天?
The dance in your honor?

992
01:17:45,296 --> 01:17:47,205
14号
On the 14th.

993
01:17:54,828 --> 01:17:59,418
下午好 Stokes先生?
Good afternoon Mr. Stokes?

994
01:18:03,768 --> 01:18:05,392
我说过别让人打扰我 姑娘
I told you I was not to be disturbed girl

995
01:18:05,473 --> 01:18:07,311
什么事?
what is it?

996
01:18:07,387 --> 01:18:11,349
夏洛克 福尔摩斯先生想见你
It's Mr. Sherlock Holmes to see you sir.

997
01:18:11,422 --> 01:18:15,834
"Aggie 我被你打动了"
"Oh Aggie, you've touched my heart."

998
01:18:15,910 --> 01:18:17,048
福尔摩斯先生?
Mr. Holmes?

999
01:18:17,128 --> 01:18:18,337
我是来通知你
I'm here to inform you

1000
01:18:18,415 --> 01:18:21,783
我的委托人已经接受了你的条件
that my client accepts your terms.

1001
01:18:21,859 --> 01:18:25,499
她的做法是明智的
She's acted with perspicacity.

1002
01:18:25,582 --> 01:18:27,764
她有个小小的请求
She begs but a small favor.

1003
01:18:27,843 --> 01:18:29,123
是什么?
What is it?

1004
01:18:29,200 --> 01:18:31,181
她想把交易延迟到15号进行
That the exchange be delayed until the 1 5th.

1005
01:18:31,253 --> 01:18:34,619
在它前一天晚上 伯爵安排了一个舞会
The Earl has arranged a dance for the previous night

1006
01:18:34,862 --> 01:18:39,313
她需要专注于那事
and she is somewhat preoccupied with that.

1007
01:18:37,202 --> 01:18:39,313
舞会 是的
The dance yes.

1008
01:18:39,394 --> 01:18:42,869
那第二天的10点
So 1 0 o'clock the following morning

1009
01:18:42,942 --> 01:18:44,923
我们交易 行吗?
we can do business?

1010
01:18:44,995 --> 01:18:46,169
7000英镑?
Seven thousand pounds?

1011
01:18:46,247 --> 01:18:47,871
对
As agreed.

1012
01:18:47,952 --> 01:18:51,071
在这还是在贝克街?
Here or at Baker's Street?

1013
01:18:51,153 --> 01:18:52,540
这里或贝克街
Here, Baker Street.

1014
01:18:52,613 --> 01:18:56,396
也许找一个中立的地方
Neutral ground perhaps.

1015
01:18:56,475 --> 01:18:58,456
Diogenes俱乐部
The Diogenes club

1016
01:18:58,528 --> 01:19:00,401
你是它的会员吧?
you are a member?

1017
01:19:02,772 --> 01:19:05,891
可以吗?
May I?

1018
01:19:05,973 --> 01:19:09,092
告诉我这种突然的转变
Tell me this sudden turnabout

1019
01:19:09,174 --> 01:19:12,127
是你的建议吗?
was it on your advice?

1020
01:19:12,201 --> 01:19:16,232
我不能让我的委托人听天由命
I could not abandon my client to her fate

1021
01:19:16,306 --> 01:19:19,708
Milverton先生 你胜利了
Mr. Milverton. You are the victor.

1022
01:19:23,924 --> 01:19:26,070
真是天赐的芳香
What a divine fragrance.

1023
01:19:35,927 --> 01:19:39,538
我去世的丈夫和我 就是她第二个家
My late husband and I were something of a second family to her

1024
01:19:39,615 --> 01:19:41,726
所以你明白我的忧虑了?
so you see my concern?

1025
01:19:43,998 --> 01:19:46,667
那个勒索她的人?
This man who is blackmailing her?

1026
01:19:46,747 --> 01:19:49,178
Charles Augustus Milverton
Charles Augustus Milverton

1027
01:19:49,251 --> 01:19:51,717
他是个画商
he's an arts dealer.

1028
01:19:51,791 --> 01:19:53,143
是的
Yes.

1029
01:19:53,217 --> 01:19:55,363
我听说过他
I've heard of him.

1030
01:19:55,444 --> 01:19:57,282
他收集流言
He's well placed to hear the gossip

1031
01:19:57,358 --> 01:19:59,990
然后作恶
and do his worst.

1032
01:20:00,071 --> 01:20:02,431
福尔摩斯先生怎么想?
What view does Mr. Holmes take of it?

1033
01:20:02,506 --> 01:20:06,468
他自有主张
Well I'm sure he has something in mind

1034
01:20:06,541 --> 01:20:08,200
但是他经常是最后才让我知道
but he seldom confides in me till the last minute.

1035
01:20:09,917 --> 01:20:12,134
福尔摩斯
Awe Holmes.

1036
01:20:12,212 --> 01:20:17,217
Swinstead女士很关心这件事
Lady Swinstead is fully primed for the situation.

1037
01:20:17,292 --> 01:20:21,146
时间快没有了
Time is running out

1038
01:20:21,223 --> 01:20:23,796
福尔摩斯先生
Mr. Holmes.

1039
01:20:23,867 --> 01:20:26,677
要是钱有问题...
If it is a question of paying the money...

1040
01:20:26,754 --> 01:20:28,450
那没必要
That will not be necessary.

1041
01:20:28,529 --> 01:20:30,960
那你能保证了?
You can give assurance then?

1042
01:20:31,034 --> 01:20:33,915
这么说可能有点轻率 Swinstead夫人
That would be unwise in me Lady Swinstead

1043
01:20:33,991 --> 01:20:36,801
但是我向您保证
but I assure you

1044
01:20:36,878 --> 01:20:39,997
我会尽我所能
I will give it my best.

1045
01:20:40,079 --> 01:20:43,139
那样我会很满意
I shall have to be satisfied with that then.

1046
01:20:47,838 --> 01:20:49,594
福尔摩斯先生
Mr. Holmes?

1047
01:20:51,769 --> 01:20:56,113
这个人一定要闭嘴
This man must be silenced.

1048
01:21:05,337 --> 01:21:07,104
她知道Milverton吗?
Does she know about Milverton?

1049
01:21:07,181 --> 01:21:08,425
他的名字?
A name?

1050
01:21:08,502 --> 01:21:10,411
是的  我告诉她了
Yes I told her.

1051
01:21:10,485 --> 01:21:12,159
我错了吗?
Was that wrong of me?

1052
01:21:14,834 --> 01:21:17,122
华生 这些钱
Oh Watson these bills,

1053
01:21:17,200 --> 01:21:19,109
必须要付
they must be paid.

1054
01:21:19,183 --> 01:21:20,842
顺便说一句 我确保了我们
Oh, incidentally I managed to secure

1055
01:21:20,922 --> 01:21:23,803
都被邀请去参见Dovercourt的舞会
an invitation for us both to the Dovercourt dance.

1056
01:21:23,880 --> 01:21:26,311
虽然离伦敦有点远
The house is some miles from London

1057
01:21:26,385 --> 01:21:29,176
但是离我的目标近了
but in reach for my purposes.

1058
01:21:30,142 --> 01:21:31,636
什么目标?
What purposes?

1059
01:21:31,707 --> 01:21:37,123
我要在那天晚上 潜入Milverton家偷窃
I intend to burgle the Milverton house that night.

1060
01:21:37,204 --> 01:21:38,627
天啊 福尔摩斯
For heaven sakes Holmes

1061
01:21:38,700 --> 01:21:40,015
想想你在干什么!
think what you're doing.

1062
01:21:45,310 --> 01:21:48,500
让我们好好地想清楚
Well let us look at it fairly and clearly.

1063
01:21:48,580 --> 01:21:49,933
你得承认
You will admit

1064
01:21:49,970 --> 01:21:53,266
这件事从道义上来说是正义的
that the cause is morally justifiable.

1065
01:21:53,346 --> 01:21:54,354
是的
Yes.

1066
01:21:54,425 --> 01:21:55,962
在法律上是犯罪
Technically criminal.

1067
01:21:56,547 --> 01:22:00,083
不过是像抢他的钱包
No more than raiding his pockets ,

1068
01:22:00,121 --> 01:22:03,285
你那时就愿意帮我
a cause which you were perfectly willing to help me.

1069
01:22:03,321 --> 01:22:04,482
那时事出突然
That was on the spurt of the moment

1070
01:22:04,519 --> 01:22:05,832
不是理智的
not on the coal light of reason.

1071
01:22:05,870 --> 01:22:07,309
理智?
Reason?

1072
01:22:09,280 --> 01:22:12,055
这件事里有"理智"的用武之地吗 华生?
Is there reasoning to be done Watson?

1073
01:22:12,133 --> 01:22:14,493
没有一样要我动脑子
Nothing to test my brain?

1074
01:22:14,569 --> 01:22:16,098
可恶
That's the curse of it.

1075
01:22:16,169 --> 01:22:18,351
想想
Think.

1076
01:22:21,630 --> 01:22:23,646
要是你被抓了
If you're caught,

1077
01:22:23,718 --> 01:22:25,247
这份令人尊敬的事业
an honored career

1078
01:22:25,318 --> 01:22:27,500
就会彻底完蛋 在公众前颜面丢尽
ending in failure and public disgrace.

1079
01:22:27,580 --> 01:22:28,682
什么完蛋 什么丢脸
What failure? What disgrace?

1080
01:22:28,718 --> 01:22:30,674
能比得上被打败?
Against defeat.

1081
01:22:31,511 --> 01:22:33,562
你再了解我不过
You know me well enough

1082
01:22:33,633 --> 01:22:37,180
如果有别的可能
that I would never adopt so objectionable a course

1083
01:22:37,251 --> 01:22:38,745
我是不会出此下策
if another were possible.

1084
01:22:38,816 --> 01:22:40,891
我必须拿到那些信
I must have those letters.

1085
01:22:40,974 --> 01:22:43,998
我对那房子了如指掌
And have the house in the palm of my hand.

1086
01:22:44,070 --> 01:22:47,130
先动手再动脑
The cudgel before the brain.

1087
01:22:50,507 --> 01:22:52,309
那讨厌的Milverton呢?
What of the odious Milverton?

1088
01:22:52,384 --> 01:22:55,813
难道他会敞开大门请你大摇大摆进去吗?
Do you think he's just going to open his gates and invite you to stroll in?

1089
01:22:55,850 --> 01:22:58,675
Milverton会去舞会
Milverton will be at the dance

1090
01:22:58,751 --> 01:23:01,253
作为Eva小姐的客人
as the guest of Lady Eva's.

1091
01:23:01,326 --> 01:23:04,421
太荒谬了 福尔摩斯
That's monstrous Holmes.

1092
01:23:04,492 --> 01:23:06,958
我赌上了自尊和名誉
My self-respect and reputation are at stake

1093
01:23:07,032 --> 01:23:08,905
这是唯一的办法
it's the only way.

1094
01:23:08,979 --> 01:23:10,437
我不喜欢这样
Well I don't like it,

1095
01:23:10,510 --> 01:23:12,039
一点也不
any of it.

1096
01:23:26,165 --> 01:23:28,146
没什么可怕的
You have nothing to fear.

1097
01:23:47,840 --> 01:23:50,580
Eva?
Eva?

1098
01:23:55,841 --> 01:23:59,767
Hudson太太  谁让你给我整理的?
Mrs. Hudson why did you tidy for me?

1099
01:23:59,842 --> 01:24:01,858
我的鞋呢?
Where the hell are my shoes?

1100
01:24:30,179 --> 01:24:31,210
鞋?
Shoes?

1101
01:24:31,292 --> 01:24:32,086
是的
Yes.

1102
01:24:32,162 --> 01:24:33,300
面具?
Masks?

1103
01:24:33,380 --> 01:24:34,660
黑丝手绢
Black silk handkerchief.

1104
01:24:34,736 --> 01:24:36,938
我看你天生就会这些事
I see you have a natural turn for this sort of thing.

1105
01:24:36,975 --> 01:24:38,804
我也很纳闷自己怎么学来的
I wonder where I learned it.

1106
01:24:50,079 --> 01:24:53,719
今晚要像平时一样小心提防
Take the usual precautions tonight.

1107
01:24:53,801 --> 01:24:56,470
Hebworth
Hebworth.

1108
01:24:56,550 --> 01:24:58,838
我会的
I will.

1109
01:24:58,915 --> 01:25:00,896
祝您愉快
Enjoy your evening.

1110
01:26:31,978 --> 01:26:33,566
这的人都有危险 福尔摩斯 (会成为下个受害者)
The people are at risks here Holmes.

1111
01:26:33,647 --> 01:26:34,750
确实是这样
Yes indeed.

1112
01:26:34,831 --> 01:26:36,669
我们8分钟后走
We leave in eight minutes.

1113
01:26:40,049 --> 01:26:41,329
打扰一下 先生
Excuse me sir,

1114
01:26:41,406 --> 01:26:43,908
夫人在楼上想见你
Her ladyship would like to see you upstairs.

1115
01:26:50,729 --> 01:26:52,110
Harry
Harry.

1116
01:26:53,478 --> 01:26:55,280
那个人
That man

1117
01:26:56,922 --> 01:26:59,626
他是被邀请的客人吗?
is he an invited guest?

1118
01:26:59,705 --> 01:27:01,958
Milverton
Milverton.

1119
01:27:02,037 --> 01:27:04,362
是的 是Eva的想法
Yes it's something Eva schemed.

1120
01:27:04,437 --> 01:27:05,860
那副画
The painting.

1121
01:27:05,933 --> 01:27:09,511
聪明的姑娘很可能 是想压低价钱才邀请他来
The old girl is probably trying to whittle down the price by inviting him here.

1122
01:27:11,046 --> 01:27:13,334
别担心 Diana
Don't worry yourself Diana.

1123
01:27:13,412 --> 01:27:15,393
没事
It's all right.

1124
01:27:52,864 --> 01:27:56,410
太奇怪了
How strange

1125
01:27:56,482 --> 01:28:00,194
在这看见你 福尔摩斯先生
to see you here Mr. Holmes.

1126
01:28:03,162 --> 01:28:06,115
生意娱乐两不误?
Mixing business with pleasure?

1127
01:28:06,189 --> 01:28:09,035
毫无疑问你也是
There's no doubt you are.

1128
01:28:09,110 --> 01:28:12,930
我今晚是纯粹来玩的 福尔摩斯 我向你保证
purely pleasure this evening Mr. Holmes I assure you

1129
01:28:14,156 --> 01:28:16,172
你会遵守我们的约定吧
You will be keeping our appointment.

1130
01:29:18,064 --> 01:29:20,246
先生
Sir.

1131
01:29:20,326 --> 01:29:22,899
我的访客半小时到
I am expecting a visitor in an half an hour.

1132
01:29:22,970 --> 01:29:24,666
是 先生
Sir.

1133
01:30:53,388 --> 01:30:56,092
主人走了 仆人就开始享乐
Servants are playing while the master's away.

1134
01:31:20,212 --> 01:31:22,014
福尔摩斯
Holmes?

1135
01:31:26,368 --> 01:31:28,099
Milvertons的马车
Milvertons carriage

1136
01:31:28,178 --> 01:31:29,731
没时间关门了
no time to lose the door.

1137
01:35:42,770 --> 01:35:45,680
你使我缩短了今晚的娱乐时间
You made me curtail my evening's entertainment.

1138
01:35:45,761 --> 01:35:48,157
我希望你证明那是值得的
I hope you prove worth it.

1139
01:35:48,231 --> 01:35:51,255
你不能挑个更适合交谈的时间来吗?
You couldn't have come at a more sociable time?

1140
01:35:51,328 --> 01:35:53,272
好吧 不行就算了吧
Well if you couldn't, you couldn't

1141
01:35:55,433 --> 01:35:58,801
要是伯爵夫人是个严厉的女主人
if the Countess is a hard mistress

1142
01:35:58,878 --> 01:36:02,590
你现在有机会报复她了
you have a chance now to get even with her.

1143
01:36:02,670 --> 01:36:05,766
上帝保佑  你怎么在发抖?
Bless the girl, what are you shivering about?

1144
01:36:06,739 --> 01:36:09,241
对!
That's right!

1145
01:36:09,315 --> 01:36:11,426
打起精神
Pull yourself together.

1146
01:36:11,506 --> 01:36:13,667
我们来谈生意
Now then, let's get down to business.

1147
01:36:15,890 --> 01:36:17,836
你说你有5封
You save you have five letters,

1148
01:36:17,873 --> 01:36:23,566
关于D' Albert伯爵夫人的信?
which compromise the Countess D' Albert?

1149
01:36:26,569 --> 01:36:28,899
你要卖 我要买
You want to sell them. I want to buy them.

1150
01:36:28,971 --> 01:36:30,429
目前为止一切顺利
So far, so good.

1151
01:36:30,501 --> 01:36:33,525
就剩下谈好价钱了
So it remains to fix the price.

1152
01:36:33,597 --> 01:36:36,337
当然我要先检查这些信
Of course I shall want to examine the letters.

1153
01:36:36,415 --> 01:36:40,518
如果内容够好...
If they prove to be good specimens then...

1154
01:37:03,621 --> 01:37:06,645
天啊 是你?
Great heavens, it is you?

1155
01:37:10,057 --> 01:37:14,777
一个被你毁了一生的女人
A woman who's life you have ruined.

1156
01:37:17,293 --> 01:37:21,426
你太固执了
You were so obstinate.

1157
01:37:21,463 --> 01:37:26,257
-12年前 法国 -为什么你要把我逼上绝路呢?
-Paris twelve years ago. -Why did you drive me to such extremities?

1158
01:37:26,293 --> 01:37:29,081
一段被尘封的往事
An episode long closed.

1159
01:37:29,157 --> 01:37:31,410
我本连一个苍蝇都不愿伤害
I wouldn't hurt a fly of my own accord.

1160
01:37:31,488 --> 01:37:33,147
你一直等待
You waited for the moment

1161
01:37:33,227 --> 01:37:35,552
直到能赢得最大的赌注的时候
when the stakes was most worth winning.

1162
01:37:35,627 --> 01:37:37,738
我能怎么做?
What was I to do?

1163
